take us to Moo, Suezo,

68
00:02:59,579 --> 00:03:01,248
so you ought to enjoy
it while you can

69
00:03:01,248 --> 00:03:03,517
'cause this is
as good as it gets.

70
00:03:03,517 --> 00:03:04,584
(exclaiming)

71
00:03:04,584 --> 00:03:06,019
We should go.

72
00:03:06,019 --> 00:03:08,388
