monsters into baddies

73
00:03:08,388 --> 00:03:11,425
so they can do his
nasty work for him.

74
00:03:11,425 --> 00:03:12,993
I will not.

75
00:03:12,993 --> 00:03:15,128
I'm with you, Golem.

76
00:03:15,128 --> 00:03:18,565
I'm ready to break loose from
these restraints any time now.

77
00:03:18,565 --> 00:03:19,866
No, don't!

78
00:03:19,866 --> 00:03:21,368
Tiger, you can't forget

79
00:03:21,368 --> 00:03:23,203
that we aren't just
acting on our own here.

80
00:03:23,203 --> 00:03:24,304
You know that if we escape

81
00:03:24,304 --> 00:03:27,074
they'll just take it
out on the others.

82
00:03:27,074 --> 00:03:29,443
And we don't have
Genki and Mocchi here

83
00:03:29,443 --> 00:03:30,744
to help either.

84
00:03:30,744 --> 00:03:33,313
No more Cherry
Blossom Blizzards,

85
00:03:33,313 --> 00:03:35,449
no more "kiss the sky."

86
